{"tid":2374744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"狗隊推出新宣傳片 涉及公帑將向立法會交代 期間動用600狗員拍攝9晚","createTime":"2021-01-21T12:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T05:55:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6f11ecc33809f64856d0b63c15879a25d50c1126","tid":2374744,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:46:02.000Z","msg":"警方推出新宣傳片 涉及成本將向立法會交代<br />\n<br />\n警方推出新宣傳片，將會在電視台及警方社交專頁播放。警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓表示，宣傳片的製作符合政府既定程序，有內部審計，並會向立法會財委會交代成本，確保公帑用得其所。<br />\n<br />\n警隊對上一年拍攝宣傳片已經是20年前。新宣傳片《守城》講述恐怖份子在本港多個地點脅持人質，警方出動多個部隊解決事件，期間出動約600名警員，涉及15個警方單位，用了9個晚上拍攝。郭嘉銓在傳媒發布會說，希望透過宣傳片表達警方專業及正面形象，帶出居安思危的意識，並對招募有正面作用。<br />\n<br />\n宣傳片去年8月開始構思，當時已頒布香港國安法，郭嘉銓說宣傳片與國安法無直接關係，只是去年8月社會開始平靜，警方有空間及時間製作。<br />\n<br />\n被問到涉及的公帑、為何選定在一個電視台播出時，郭嘉銓說，導演林超賢的製作團隊以「友情價」接拍，只有一間公司投標，製作過程涉及不少商業機構，不可以公開合約資料，現階段不能透露具體數額。他又說，歡迎其他傳媒申請轉播，但不透露與電視台播放的協定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571654-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571654-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=419141c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571654-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1081e42e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571654-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"91c9c5ad25ac3d0771194df34d8592068e26a5e2","tid":2374744,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:49:30.000Z","msg":"期間動用600隻狗，拍狗晚"},{"pid":"bc523e0e9b432d483f52049d2b5bd1b28b0615f9","tid":2374744,"uid":9,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:50:27.000Z","msg":"明正言順呃ot"},{"pid":"895c622990d0466bdae4ee5f53258dc601dcde1e","tid":2374744,"uid":242323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:52:10.000Z","msg":"林超賢<br />\n同得一間藍屍公司投標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fe02aba2dc95701e60dbf64911ae4f3d20cdae","tid":2374744,"uid":38177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:52:38.000Z","msg":"又呃一筆"},{"pid":"7b6ac9cf3875774cde61af28433979ae976daa82","tid":2374744,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:53:24.000Z","msg":"拎市民既錢去呃市民，買武器打鳩市民"},{"pid":"581f9bd4348013cc6a6f96f0d0be797cfd7e8452","tid":2374744,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"表演耍雜技？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e04cad308367b2e57fdbe364dcc0e76f85c7be0","tid":2374744,"uid":106408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc523e0e9b432d483f52049d2b5bd1b28b0615f9","tid":2374744,"uid":9,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:50:27.000Z","msg":"明正言順呃ot"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:55:31.000Z","msg":"食過返尋味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}